Name: DenyHost
Version: 2.9
Summary: DenyHost is a utility to help sys admins thwart ssh hackers
Home-page: https://github.com/Wexsz0801/DenyHosts_SEU
Author: Wexsz0801
Author-email: wexsz0801@example.com
License: GPL v2
Description: 
        DenyHost is a python program that automatically blocks ssh attacks by adding entries to
        /etc/hosts.deny. DenyHosts will also inform Linux administrators about offending hosts, attacked
        users and suspicious logins.
        Originally authored by Phil Schwartz.
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
